# ============================================
# KEEP THESE FILES FOR USERS:
# ============================================
# ✅ lib/ (all source code)
# ✅ assets/ (config.json, etc.)
# ✅ packages/ (patched bluetooth package)
# ✅ pubspec.yaml (dependencies)
# ✅ android/app/build.gradle.kts (SDK 36 config)
# ✅ android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml (permissions)
# ✅ android/build.gradle.kts (root gradle config)
# ✅ android/settings.gradle.kts (gradle settings)
# ✅ android/gradle.properties (gradle properties)
# ✅ README.md (documentation)
# ✅ SETUP_GUIDE.md (quick setup)
# ✅ test/ (optional tests)
# ✅ .gitignore (this file)

# ============================================
# USER SETUP STEPS:
# ============================================
# 1. flutter create your_project_name
# 2. Copy lib/, assets/, packages/, pubspec.yaml
# 3. Replace android/app/build.gradle.kts
# 4. Replace android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml
# 5. flutter pub get
# 6. flutter run
